import React from "react";
import { TextField } from "@material-ui/core";

function DadosEntrega() {
  return (
    <form>
      <TextField
        id="cep"
        label="CEP"
        type="number"
        variant="outlined"
        margin="normal"
        
      />
            <TextField
        id="endereco"
        label="Endereco"
        type="text"
        variant="outlined"
        margin="normal"
        fullWidth
      />
            <TextField
        id="numero"
        label="Numero"
        type="number"
        variant="outlined"
        margin="normal"
        
      />
                  <TextField
        id="estado"
        label="Estado"
        type="text"
        variant="outlined"
        margin="normal"
        
      />

<TextField
        id="cidade"
        label="Cidade"
        type="text"
        variant="outlined"
        margin="normal"
        
      />
      
    </form>
  );
}

export default DadosEntrega;
